OL,3,C'Shell have continually destroyed
OL,4,Ceverything': Toxic legacy of oil in
OL,5,CNigeria
OL,7,FThe discovery of precious resources
OL,8,Fshould be a blessing and change the
OL,9,Ffortunes of nations and their people.
OL,11,FBut in the region of the Niger Delta
OL,12,Fin Nigeria, known as Ogoniland, the
OL,13,Fdiscovery of large quantities of crude
OL,14,Foil nearly 70 years ago has left a
OL,15,Fpainful legacy for many communities
OL,16,Famongst them - the Ogalie and Bille
OL,17,Fpeople, and also now for the giant oil
OL,18,Fcompany Shell.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/18
