OL,4,Ceverything': Toxic legacy of oil in
OL,5,CNigeria
OL,7,FNiger Delta has just one large
OL,8,Funderground source of fresh water but
OL,9,Fit has been contaminated in the search
OL,10,Fand production of that other vastly
OL,11,Fmore precious liquid: crude oil.
OL,13,FResidents have no drinking water, left
OL,14,Fgagging at the smell of oil in what
OL,15,Fshould be a source of clean water.
