OL,4,Ceverything': Toxic legacy of oil in
OL,5,CNigeria
OL,7,FThe Ogale community say the extraction
OL,8,Fof crude oil, also known as "black
OL,9,Fgold", has destroyed the mangroves
OL,10,Fthat once provided rich sources of
OL,11,Fplants and fruit, whilst polluting the
OL,12,Fwaterways and killing the huge marine
OL,13,Fresources, especially fish, which
OL,14,Fsustained communities and livelihoods.
OL,16,FAn Ogale farmer Chief Fortune Olaka
OL,17,Fspoke to ITV News about the
OL,18,Fdevastating effect the spill has had
OL,19,Fon agriculture.
