OL,3,C'Shell have continually destroyed
OL,4,Ceverything': Toxic legacy of oil in
OL,5,CNigeria
OL,7,F"It has affected our land, affected
OL,8,Four drinking water, affected our
OL,9,Fstream, affected our rivers, killed
OL,10,Fanimals in our bush, killed our
OL,11,Feconomic trees, damaged our stream and
OL,12,Fkilled the fish that are in the stream
OL,13,Ftoday.
OL,15,F"We don't have means of livelihood in
OL,16,Fthis community. We are suffering for
OL,17,Fwater to drink."
