OL,7,FThe United Nations Environment
OL,8,FProgramme (UNEP) found that the oil
OL,9,Fcontamination in the community's
OL,10,Fgroundwater was 1,000 times higher
OL,11,Fthan the levels allowed in Nigerian
OL,12,Flaw.
OL,14,FThe Ogale and Bille communities in the
OL,15,FNiger Delta, a combined population of
OL,16,F80,000, have allegedly suffered from
OL,17,Fhundreds of spills which have left
OL,18,Fthem without clean water, unable to
OL,19,Ffarm or fish, and created serious
OL,20,Frisks to public health.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/18
