OL,7,FBut today, this contest between a
OL,8,Fsmall African community in a corner of
OL,9,FNigeria and a giant global
OL,10,Fcorporation, involving a history of
OL,11,Fthirty years of spills, comes to The
OL,12,FRoyal Courts of Justice in London -
OL,13,Fwhere after a decade-long battle
OL,14,Fagainst the multinational company
OL,15,FShell and its Nigerian subsidiary, the
OL,16,FOgale and Bille people are having
OL,17,Ftheir case for compensation heard.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/18
