OL,7,F"I was born in the 50s, we gave them
OL,8,Feverything. My people were submissive
OL,9,Fto them, hospitable to them," he said.
OL,11,FNow, that seems like a distant memory.
OL,13,FWhen I asked him what he hopes for the
OL,14,Ffuture, his request is simple.
OL,15,F"Justice."
OL,17,FMr Okpabi said to him justice means
OL,18,Ftalking to the community and sitting
OL,19,Fdown with their lawyers.
