OL,7,F"You are paying millions of pounds to
OL,8,Frun away from somebody you poisoned,"
OL,9,Fhe added.
OL,11,F"The way of life I lived in my teens,
OL,12,Fmy sons, I have five of them don't
OL,13,Fhave that opportunity anymore. How can
OL,14,Fyou quantify that loss? How can you
OL,15,Fpay for that damage? It's
OL,16,Funquantifiable."
OL,18,FShell is planning to sell its Nigerian
OL,19,Fsubsidiary to Renaissance Africa, a
OL,20,Fconsortium of local and international
OL,21,Fcompanies.
