OL,7,FThis leaves the local community
OL,8,Fanxiously waiting to see who will
OL,9,Fsupport them in their efforts to clean-
OL,10,Fup their homeland.
OL,12,F"How come now you're running away from
OL,13,Fall you have cost us? How can you say
OL,14,Fyou are not responsible for bringing
OL,15,Fout the crude? You are the operator.
OL,16,FYou brought out the crude," Mr Okpabi
OL,17,Fsaid.
