OL,7,F"The crude was there, God gave it to
OL,8,Fus, it wasn't killing us. When you
OL,9,Fwere not there, you came in, now
OL,10,Fbrought it. You should have the
OL,11,Fresponsibility of bringing out the
OL,12,Fbest technology."
OL,14,FShell does not deny the extreme
OL,15,Fcontamination of Ogoniland but denies
