OL,7,FInstead, the company says that the oil
OL,8,Fspills have been caused by sabotage,
OL,9,Ftheft and illegal refining by the
OL,10,Fcommunities in the region, who have
OL,11,Ffor decades sought to steal crude oil
OL,12,Ffrom their pipelines to sell in local
OL,13,Fmarkets.
OL,15,FShell argues that they should not be
OL,16,Fliable for the contamination and
OL,17,Fdamage caused.
