OL,7,FShell told ITV News: "Oil spills
OL,8,Fcaused by sabotage, crude oil theft
OL,9,Fand illegal refining are major sources
OL,10,Fof pollution in the areas concerned.
OL,11,FShell plc and SPDC maintain that they
OL,12,Fcannot be held liable for this
OL,13,Fpollution."
OL,15,FYears of living with oil pollution has
OL,16,Fmade the local community in the Niger
OL,17,FDelta determined.
OL,19,FThey have nowhere near the resources
OL,20,Fthat Shell has to fight legal battles
OL,21,Ffor years.
