OL,7,FBut they say they want to force Shell
OL,8,Fto at least help them recover the
OL,9,Fprimary sources of livelihood for
OL,10,Ftheir villages - the mangroves and
OL,11,Fpolluted waters that have destroyed
OL,12,Ftheir fishing industry.
OL,14,FNo single oil leak is to blame, but
OL,15,Fthe UK law firm Leigh Day who are
OL,16,Facting for the Ogale and Bille
OL,17,Fcommunities are taking Shell to court
OL,18,Ffor what they claim is a case of
OL,19,Fsystemic failure spanning over 70
OL,20,Fyears.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/18
