OL,7,FThe heart of their legal argument is
OL,8,Fthat UK law should change its systems
OL,9,Fof accountability, making a company
OL,10,Fliable for the human rights
OL,11,Fprotections of a community and its
OL,12,Faccess to a healthy environment.
OL,14,FIn essence saying that the right to a
OL,15,Fhealthy environment is a fundamental
OL,16,Fhuman right.
