OL,7,FThe question of who is to blame
OL,8,Fultimately goes beyond the High Court.
OL,9,FIs it Shell who didn't make the
OL,10,Finvestments needed to maintain the oil
OL,11,Finfrastructure in an area of Nigeria
OL,12,Fwith rising?
OL,14,FOr is it the criminal groups that
OL,15,Fsteal the oil by damaging the breaking
OL,16,Fthe pipelines?
OL,18,FOr is it successive Nigerian
OL,19,Fgovernment and politicians who didn't
OL,20,Fintervene as the regulators to find a
OL,21,Fway out of this situation?
